{"tid":1439335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"製作長輩圖教學","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:32:30.000Z","uid":61886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"987ff7a0f6c674383d52425990af777ec9ba7a10","tid":1439335,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"與其自己等人出圖<br />\n不如自己學整長輩圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n製作軟件<br />\n- 電腦用powerpoint<br />\n- 手機用Spark Post<br />\n<br />\n背景<br />\n- 荷花蓮花圖<br />\n- 觀音圖<br />\n- 風景圖<br />\n- 不建議加入集會或示威圖片<br />\n<br />\n內容<br />\n- 不用詳細論述或分析<br />\n- 前因及後理不需有必然因果關係<br />\n- 強調「結果」<br />\n- 提出陰謀論<br />\n- 不用下判斷，旨在混淆思考<br />\n- 忌用「悔氣」語調<br />\n例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYgjR5h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYgjR5h.png&h=51211646&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/csATWwY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcsATWwY.png&h=39638887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前因同後果係無因果關係<br />\n亦未必需要係事實<br />\n提出疑問混淆思考即可<br />\n<br />\n排版<br />\n- 字型要夠大，唔使伸個頭埋去先睇到<br />\n- 不要長篇論述<br />\n- 字顏色要清晰，勿用粉色系<br />\n<br />\n每人都可以係文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8924d9bf6fb13d59eb03040690d832befb7baa","tid":1439335,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"推 powerpoint好洗好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3fb641bcf17ce35ec6b9b968f5357ae640e18b","tid":1439335,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"廢老好多都好自大<br />\n唔鐘意人地教佢野<br />\n所以佢地最鐘意陰謀論<br />\n覺得自己好有獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b9a3270d2b8046c99b87b9b93bb510cac76f1d","tid":1439335,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}